  "description": "A pipeline monitoring component that detects anomalies in numeric output values using \nstatistical methods. It supports Z-Score, IQR (Interquartile Range), and Rolling Average \ndeviation detection with configurable sensitivity and window sizes. Detected anomalies are \nclassified by severity (normal, warning, critical) and added to document metadata.</br>\n</br>\nUse this node to monitor pipeline outputs for unexpected patterns, outliers, or shifts \nin data distribution that may indicate issues requiring attention.",
